_['proj_detail_repaw']=['RePaw is a Django REST API powering both a mobile app and a Django webapp about dogs. Connects dog owners with services like grooming, walking, boarding, and veterinary care.','Το RePaw είναι ένα Django REST API που τροφοδοτεί εφαρμογή για κινητά και webapp για σκύλους. Συνδέει ιδιοκτήτες με υπηρεσίες φροντίδας.','RePaw è un API REST Django per app mobile e webapp sui cani. Collega proprietari con servizi di cura.','RePaw, mobil uygulama ve Django web uygulamasini calistiran bir Django REST API\'sidir. Kopek sahiplerini bakim hizmetleriyle bulusturur.','RePaw este un API REST Django care alimenteaza o aplicatie mobila si o webapp Django despre caini. Conecteaza proprietarii cu servicii de ingrijire.','RePaw eshte nje API REST Django qe mundeson nje aplikacion mobil dhe nje webapp Django per qen. Lidh pronaret me sherbime kujdesi.','RePaw e Django REST API, koeto dava energiia na mobilno prilozhenie i Django webapp za kucheta.','RePaw es una API REST Django que impulsa una app movil y una webapp Django sobre perros. Conecta duenos con servicios de cuidado.','RePaw est une API REST Django alimentant une app mobile et une webapp Django pour chiens. Relie les proprietaires aux services de soins.'];
_['proj_detail_finance']=['A comprehensive Django finance app. Track income/expenses, categorize transactions, view spending analytics with charts, and manage budgets with recurring transactions and multi-account support.','Μια ολοκληρωμένη εφαρμογή Django για οικονομικά. Παρακολουθήστε έσοδα/έξοδα, κατηγοριοποιήστε συναλλαγές και διαχειριστείτε προϋπολογισμούς.','Un\'app Django completa per le finanze. Tieni traccia di entrate/uscite, categorizza transazioni e gestisci budget.','Kapsamli bir Django finans uygulamasi. Gelir/gider takibi, islem kategorizasyonu ve butce yonetimi.','O aplicatie Django cuprinzatoare pentru finante. Urmariti venituri/cheltuieli si gestionati bugete.','Nje aplikacion gjitheperfshires Django per financat. Gjurmoni te ardhura/shpenzime dhe menaxhoni buxhete.','Izcherpatelno Django prilozhenie za finansi. Prosledyavai prihodi/razhodi i upravlyavai byudzheti.','Una aplicacion Django completa para finanzas. Seguimiento de ingresos/gastos y gestion de presupuestos.','Une application Django complete pour les finances. Suivez les revenus/depenses et geerez les budgets.'];
_['proj_detail_ur8']=['A full-stack video platform inspired by YouTube. Supports upload and streaming via FFmpeg, user channels, subscriptions, comments, likes/dislikes, and playlists with PostgreSQL and Redis.','Μια full-stack πλατφόρμα βίντεο εμπνευσμένη από το YouTube. Υποστηρίζει ανέβασμα και ροή μέσω FFmpeg.','Una piattaforma video full-stack ispirata a YouTube. Supporta upload e streaming via FFmpeg.','YouTube\'dan ilham alan full-stack video platformu. FFmpeg ile yukleme ve akis destegi.','O platforma video full-stack inspirata de YouTube. Suporta incarcare si streaming prin FFmpeg.','Nje platforme video full-stack e frymezuar nga YouTube. Mbeshtet ngarkim dhe transmetim permes FFmpeg.','Full-stack video platforma, vdahnovera ot YouTube. Podkarya kachvane i streaming chrez FFmpeg.','Una plataforma de video full-stack inspirada en YouTube. Soporta carga y transmision via FFmpeg.','Une plateforme video full-stack inspiree de YouTube. Supporte le telechargement et le streaming via FFmpeg.'];
_['proj_detail_pixelsprint']=['A full-featured task management app inspired by Agile. Teams create sprints, manage tasks on boards, track progress, and collaborate in real-time with Django, Celery, Bulma, and HTMX.','Μια πλήρης εφαρμογή διαχείρισης εργασιών εμπνευσμένη από Agile. Ομάδες δημιουργούν sprints και συνεργάζονται σε πραγματικό χρόνο.','Un\'app completa per la gestione delle attivita ispirata ad Agile. I team creano sprint e collaborano in tempo reale.','Agile\'dan ilham alan tam donanimli bir gorev yonetimi uygulamasi. Ekipler sprint olusturur ve gercek zamanli isbirligi yapar.','O aplicatie completa de gestionare a sarcinilor inspirata de Agile. Echipele creeaza sprint-uri si colaboreaza in timp real.','Nje aplikacion i plote per menaxhimin e detyrave i frymezuar nga Agile. Ekipet krijojne sprinte dhe bashkepuntojne ne kohe reale.','Polnofunktsionalno prilozhenie za upravlenie na zadachi, vdahnoveno ot Agile. Ekipi suzdavat sprintove i si satrudnichat v realno vreme.','Una aplicacion completa de gestion de tareas inspirada en Agile. Los equipos crean sprints y colaboran en tiempo real.','Une application complete de gestion de taches inspiree d\'Agile. Les equipes creent des sprints et collaborent en temps reel.'];
_['proj_detail_pypong']=['Classic Pong recreated with PyGame in under 3 hours. Features single-player AI, two-player local multiplayer, score tracking, and increasing difficulty.','Κλασικό Pong με PyGame σε λιγότερο από 3 ώρες. AI ενός παίκτη, τοπικό multiplayer και προοδευτική δυσκολία.','Pong classico ricreato con PyGame in meno di 3 ore. AI singolo giocatore e multiplayer locale.','3 saatten kisa surede PyGame ile yeniden olusturulan klasik Pong. Tek oyunculu AI ve yerel multiplayer.','Pong clasic recreat cu PyGame in sub 3 ore. AI pentru un jucator si multiplayer local.','Pong klasik i rikrijuar me PyGame ne me pak se 3 ore. AI per nje lojtar dhe multiplayer lokal.','Klasicheski Pong, preasazdan s PyGame za po-malko ot 3 chasa. AI za edin igrach i lokalen multiplayer.','Pong clasico recreado con PyGame en menos de 3 horas. IA para un jugador y multijugador local.','Pong classique recree avec PyGame en moins de 3 heures. IA pour un joueur et multijoueur local.'];
_['proj_detail_photofav']=['Angular/TypeScript photo gallery with image upload, album management, favorites system, and comprehensive end-to-end testing using TestBed and SCSS.','Γκαλερί φωτογραφιών Angular/TypeScript με ανέβασμα εικόνων, διαχείριση άλμπουμ και end-to-end δοκιμές.','Galleria foto Angular/TypeScript con upload immagini, gestione album e test end-to-end.','Angular/TypeScript fotograf galerisi. Goruntu yukleme, album yonetimi ve kapsamli test.','Galerie foto Angular/TypeScript cu upload imagini, gestionare albume si testare end-to-end.','Galeri fotografish Angular/TypeScript me ngarkim imazhesh, menaxhim albumesh dhe testim end-to-end.','Foto galeriya Angular/TypeScript s kachvane na izobrazheniya, upravlenie na albumi i end-to-end testove.','Galeria de fotos Angular/TypeScript con carga de imagenes, gestion de albumes y pruebas end-to-end.','Galerie photo Angular/TypeScript avec telechargement d\'images, gestion d\'albums et tests end-to-end.'];
_['proj_detail_speech']=['ML project recognizing spoken digits (0-9) using FSDD. Features extracted with librosa (MFCC, chroma, mel-spectrogram) and classified with a Keras neural network. Real-time prediction via pyaudio.','ML έργο αναγνώρισης ψηφίων (0-9) με FSDD. Χαρακτηριστικά εξάγονται με librosa και ταξινομούνται με Keras. Πρόβλεψη σε πραγματικό χρόνο μέσω pyaudio.','Progetto ML per riconoscere cifre (0-9) con FSDD. Caratteristiche estratte con librosa e classificate con Keras. Previsione in tempo reale via pyaudio.','FSDD ile konusulan rakamlari (0-9) taniyan ML projesi. Ozellikler librosa ile cikarilir ve Keras ile siniflandirilir.','Proiect ML pentru recunoasterea cifrelor (0-9) folosind FSDD. Caracteristici extrase cu librosa si clasificate cu Keras.','Projekt ML per njohjen e shifrave (0-9) duke perdorur FSDD. Karakteristika te nxjerra me librosa dhe te klasifikuara me Keras.','ML proekt za razpoznavane na cifri (0-9) s FSDD. Harakteristiki, izvlecheni s librosa i klasifitsirani s Keras.','Proyecto ML que reconoce digitos (0-9) usando FSDD. Caracteristicas extraidas con librosa y clasificadas con Keras.','Projet ML reconnaissant les chiffres (0-9) avec FSDD. Caracteristiques extraites avec librosa et classifiees avec Keras.'];
_['proj_detail_kivy']=['A Kivy-based desktop app that downloads YouTube videos and audio at up to 8K resolution and 320kbps bitrate. Supports single video and full playlist downloads with format selection (mp4, webm, mkv, mp3). Built with yt-dlp and FFmpeg for maximum compatibility. Cross-platform on Windows, macOS, and Linux.','Μια εφαρμογή Kivy που κατεβάζει βίντεο και ήχο YouTube έως 8K και 320kbps. Υποστηρίζει μεμονωμένα βίντεο και πλήρεις λίστες αναπαραγωγής με επιλογή μορφής.','Un\'app Kivy per scaricare video e audio YouTube fino a 8K e 320kbps. Supporta video singoli e playlist con selezione del formato.','8K\'ya ve 320kbps\'e kadar YouTube video ve ses indiren Kivy tabanli bir masaustu uygulamasi. Tekli video ve tum oynatma listelerini destekler.','O aplicatie desktop Kivy pentru descarcarea videoclipurilor si audio-ului YouTube pana la 8K si 320kbps. Suporta videoclipuri individuale si playlisturi.','Nje aplikacion desktop Kivy per shkarkim video dhe audio YouTube deri ne 8K dhe 320kbps. Mbeshtet video te vetme dhe playliste te plota.','Kivy desktop prilozhenie za izteglyane na YouTube video i audio do 8K i 320kbps. Podkarya edinichni video i tsyali playlisti.','Una app de escritorio Kivy para descargar video y audio de YouTube hasta 8K y 320kbps. Soporta videos individuales y listas de reproduccion.','Une application desktop Kivy pour telecharger des videos et audio YouTube jusqu\'a 8K et 320kbps. Prend en charge les videos individuelles et les playlists.'];
_['proj_detail_tournaments']=['A TypeScript sport tournament organizer for creating and managing brackets, team registration, match scheduling, and score tracking. Supports single-elimination, double-elimination, and round-robin formats. Built with a clean, responsive interface.','Μια εφαρμογή TypeScript για διοργάνωση αθλητικών τουρνουά με δημιουργία bracket, εγγραφή ομάδων, προγραμματισμό αγώνων και παρακολούθηση σκορ. Υποστηρίζει πολλαπλές μορφές.','Un organizer di tornei sportivi TypeScript per creare bracket, registrare squadre, programmare partite e tracciare punteggi. Supporta piu formati.','TypeScript spor turnuva duzenleyicisi. Bracket olusturma, takim kaydi, mac programlama ve skor takibi.','Un organizer de turnee sportive TypeScript pentru crearea de bracket-uri, inscrierea echipelor, programarea meciurilor si urmarirea scorurilor.','Nje organizator turneesh sportiv TypeScript per krijimin e bracket-eve, regjistrimin e ekipeve, planifikimin e ndeshjeve dhe ndjekjen e rezultateve.','TypeScript organizator na sportni turniri sa sazdavane na bracket, registratsiya na otbori i proglezhdane na rezultati.','Un organizador de torneos deportivos TypeScript para crear brackets, registrar equipos, programar partidos y seguir puntuaciones.','Un organisateur de tournois sportifs TypeScript pour creer des brackets, inscrire des equipes, programmer des matchs et suivre les scores.'];
_['proj_detail_cryptdb']=['Proof-of-concept encrypted database server processing queries over encrypted data. Demonstrates techniques for query execution while maintaining data privacy and security.','Αποδεικτικός κρυπτογραφημένος διακομιστής βάσης δεδομένων. Διατηρεί το απόρρητο και την ασφάλεια των δεδομένων.','Server database crittografato proof-of-concept. Mantiene la privacy e la sicurezza dei dati.','Proof-concept sifrelenmis veritabani sunucusu. Veri gizliligini ve guvenligini korur.','Server baza de date criptata proof-of-concept. Mentine confidentialitatea si securitatea datelor.','Server i koduar i bazes se te dhenave proof-of-concept. Ruan privatensine dhe sigurine e te dhenave.','Proof-of-concept kriptiran survar za baza danni. Zapazva konfidentsialnostta i sigurnostta na dannite.','Servidor de base de datos encriptado proof-of-concept. Mantiene la privacidad y seguridad de los datos.','Serveur de base de donnees chiffre proof-of-concept. Maintient la confidentialite et la securite des donnees.'];
_['proj_detail_asteroid']=['Python space shooter where players navigate a spacecraft through asteroid fields, shoot obstacles, and score points. Features progressive difficulty, particle effects, and responsive controls.','Διαστημικό shooter Python με πλοήγηση διαστημοπλοίου, βολές εμποδίων και προοδευτική δυσκολία.','Space shooter Python con navigazione astronave e difficolta progressiva.','Python uzay aticisi. Oyuncular uzay gemisiyle asteroit alanlarinda gezinir ve puan toplar.','Space shooter Python cu navigare nava spatiala si dificultate progresiva.','Gjuajtes hapesinor Python me navigim anijeje dhe veshtiresi progresive.','Kosmicheski shooter na Python s navigatsiya na kosmicheski korab i progresivna trudnost.','Space shooter en Python con navegacion de nave espacial y dificultad progresiva.','Space shooter en Python avec navigation de vaisseau spatial et difficulte progressive.'];
